title: r/Choosingbeggars She Wanted Me To Mail My Dog to Her!
description:
r/Choosingbeggars The woman in today's episode sees a really cute dog on Instagram. Instead of being like a normal person and saying, "Hey, cute dog," this choosing beggar demands that OP send her the dog! She actually expects OP to ship her the dog like it's some sort of Amazon delivery. WTF? If you like this podcast and want to see more, follow my podcast for more daily Reddit content!
